description: CleanDS is a lightweight Python framework for statistical modeling and machine learning. It supports regression, classification, clustering, shrinkage, ensembles, distributions, and dimension reduction with a unified API, formula notation, and model selection tools.

Biased AI is a framework designed to analyze and detect biases in machine learning and AI models. OIKAN is designed to make machine learning models both accurate and Interpretable.
